data.description: Own In Ogden qualifying home.  Buyer's may be able to qualify for up to $20,000.00 with this program. Welcome home to this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom updated home. This home has been lovingly cared for over the years and has all the updates you're looking for.  The home was gutted to the studs and rebuilt from the inside in 2020 with new plumbing, electrical, and HVAC Ducting.  Also new insulation in walls, sheetrock, doors, including  an updated kitchen, and updated bathrooms.  The moment you walk through the front door, you'll be greeted by the warm glow of the hardwood floors.  It's the perfect place to relax and unwind after a long day. The updated kitchen is perfect for cooking up delicious meals. The updated bathrooms are spacious and luxurious and the corner lot provides plenty of space.  The majestic shade tree in the front yard offers a canopy that is unmatched. This tree is a symbol of strength and resilience.  If you are looking for a home that is both beautiful and functional, then this is the perfect place for you. This home is more than just a place to live, it's a place to create memories that will last a lifetime.  Only one block from Lorin Farr Park and the infamous pool of the hit movie "The Sandlot" along with the Pioneer Days Rodeo Stadium. Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from County Records .  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
